  <p>
      <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_high_intensity_focused_ultrasound">High Intensity Focused Ultrasound</xref>
 (
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_high_intensity_focused_ultrasound">HIFU</xref>
) is a medical procedure using high-intensity focused ultrasound to heat and destroy pathogenic (diseased) 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_tissue">TISSUE</xref>
 rapidly.  </p>
